/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a panoramic view of a bustling street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a pedestrian's viewpoint on the sidewalk, immersing the viewer in the city's daily life. The street is flanked by towering buildings and lush green trees, creating a harmonious blend of urban and natural elements. The sky above is a clear blue, dotted with fluffy white clouds, adding a serene backdrop to the dynamic cityscape. Power lines crisscross above the street, a common sight in many urban areas. The image is taken from a low angle, which enhances the grandeur of the buildings and the vastness of the sky.
